videos.description: After a steal, Wisconsin's D'Mitrik Trice gets his layup rejected off the backboard by Xavier Tillman on the fast break.
videos.headline: Tillman swats Trice's layup attempt

videos.description: Ethan Happ scores a bucket to reach 2,000 career points and become the 4th Big Ten player to reach 2,000 points and 1,000 rebounds.
videos.headline: Happ reaches 2,000 career points
